{
  "name": "claude-agents-dashboard",
  "description": "A live, always-open monitor for parallel Claude Code sessions, showing per-session project, git branch, model, context usage, and current tool activity by tail-reading ~/.claude/projects transcripts off disk every 3s (no daemon, no hooks). Includes a read-only Management config browser and an Analytics tab of session post-mortems.",
